<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="9Jun1936"><font color="red">9 June 1936</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I believe I can cover most of the expenses of publication of my daughter&apos;s alphabet. My idea is not to persuade her that she is a Cezanne but that on her 29th birthday &hellip; she may see something that may persuade her that her whole life has not been a failure. </div>
